item.description: Boyu Cai is a Dalian Maritime University students. He is interested in the software development and he is studying Java hard and hopes to find relevant internships. Profile He is happy with his current study, but also willing to take new challenges if the opportunity matches his interest. And he likes to make like-minded friends. Hobby While he is not studying, he enjoys watching movies, music, basketball, travelling, writing blogs and learning languages.
